    public class GeoLocationActivity
extends androidx.appcompat.app.AppCompatActivity
implements android.location.LocationListener
    GeoLocationActivity is the activity that is responsible for displaying the map and the user's location on the map. It also has the ability to add a marker to the map and save the location of the marker to the database.

      • addMarkersInRange

        Parameters:
        map - the map object which represents the osmdroid map
